# Server-Side Development Guidelines

## WebSocket Server Standards
- Implement proper connection management
- Handle disconnections gracefully
- Implement proper error handling
- Use appropriate scaling strategies

## Game State Management
- Implement proper state synchronization
- Use efficient data structures for game state
- Implement proper conflict resolution
- Handle race conditions appropriately

## Performance Optimization
- Optimize message handling
- Implement proper caching strategies
- Monitor server resources
- Implement rate limiting where necessary

## Security Guidelines
- Validate all incoming data
- Implement proper authentication
- Protect against common vulnerabilities
- Use secure WebSocket connections

## Error Handling
- Implement comprehensive error logging
- Use proper error recovery strategies
- Implement circuit breakers where appropriate
- Monitor and alert on critical errors

## Code Organization
- Use proper modular architecture
- Implement clean separation of concerns
- Follow Node.js best practices
- Use proper dependency injection

## Testing and Monitoring
- Implement proper logging strategy
- Add monitoring for critical metrics
- Write unit and integration tests
- Implement proper stress testing
